data.text:
Suman is a AAP candidate from Malleshwaram constituency in the 2023 Karnataka Assembly elections. Her profession according to the election affidavit filed with the Election Commission is: Freelance Journalism Catering Services. Suman's educational qualifications are: Others and is 50 years old.

Her total declared assets are Rs 5.6 crore which includes Rs 1.6 crore in moveable assets and Rs 4 crore as immoveable assets. Her total declared income is Rs 14.7 lakh of which Rs 7.8 lakh is self income. Suman's has total liabilities of Rs 1.3 crore.

This AAP candidate, in the election affidavit mentioned 0 criminal cases registered against her.

Candidates contesting in the 2023 Karnataka Assembly elections from Malleshwaram are: Dr Ashwath Narayan C N (BJP), Anoop Iyengar (INC), Abdul Suhail Ahmed (BSP), Uthkarsh A (JDS), Sunil Hebbi (NPP), Suman (AAP), Krishnaiah (RSDR), Rajesh B (KRS), Santosh S (BPKP), K M Fayaz Ahmed (IND), Manu Kumar (IND)

Follow the live updating tables to know the live election result status of Suman (AAP) in 2023 Malleshwaram elections.
